red loadX(0, 1 2, 3 4) x vect(0)(x) vect(0 0) (x) vect(0 0) == vect(0)(x) vect(0 0) (x) vect(0 0) .
red loadX(0, 1 2, 3 4) x vect(1)(x) vect(0 1) (x) vect(0 0) == vect(1)(x) vect(0 1) (x) vect(0 1) .
